    <para id="id4063379">IV. CONCLUSIONS</para>
    <para id="id4413355">Technological developments, such as the use of modulation for signal transmission, can have enormous social implications. The development of telegraphy, telephony, radio, TV, and now the internet, cable TV, and cellular phones have revolutionized how people relate to each other world wide.</para><para id="element-474"><link resource="ps10.pdf">Exercises .</link>
</para><para id="element-47"><link resource="ps10sol.pdf"> Solutions of Exercises.</link>
